+# TextCaretInfoCaret Object
+
+* `visible` boolean - Whether a caret or active selection edge is currently
+  visible and valid.
+* `bounds` [Rectangle](rectangle.md) - The visual rectangle of the text
+  insertion caret or active selection edge. Coordinates are in WebContents
+  viewport DIP coordinates.
+* `screenBounds` [Rectangle](rectangle.md) (optional) - The same caret rectangle
+  in screen DIP coordinates, when available.
